parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The melting dashboard can cause a glare on the windshield, obstructing the driver's vision, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The dashboard becomes soft
sticky
and shiny
causing a glare on the windshield
making it difficult to see while driving. In some cases
the dashboard may crack
release toxic fumes
or produce a noxious odor.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The melting dashboard can cause a glare on the windshield, reducing visibility and increasing the risk of accidents. The sticky surface can also be a distraction while driving, and the potential release of toxic fumes can be harmful to occupants.
symptoms: The dashboard is sticky
shiny
and melting; glare on the windshield; difficulty seeing while driving; unpleasant odor; and potential health issues due to toxic fumes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the OCS can cause the passenger airbag to malfunction, leading to injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The passenger airbag off light is illuminated on the dashboard
the airbag warning light is blinking
the passenger airbag does not deploy in an accident
the seat sensor is faulty
and the passenger airbag light stays on even when a passenger is present.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle's RPMs shoot up to 3-4 when putting the car in drive
the vehicle is slow to accelerate
and the turn signals do not turn off automatically.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The melting of the dashboard can cause a reflection on the windshield, leading to reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The top of the dashboard is melting
causing a severe reflection on the windshield
and the airbag light is on.
